<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Noticias Nueva Asunción</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  background: #0f172a;
  color: #e2e8f0;
}

header {
  padding: 40px 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b, #020617);
}

header h1 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 32px;
}

header p {
  opacity: 0.7;
}

nav {
  background: #020617;
  padding: 12px;
  text-align: center;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
}

nav a {
  color: #38bdf8;
  margin: 0 12px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.container {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: auto;
  padding: 20px;
}

.hero {
  background: #1e293b;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero h2 {
  margin-top: 0;
}

.grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 15px;
}

.card {
  background: #020617;
  padding: 15px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #1e293b;
  transition: 0.2s;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  border-color: #38bdf8;
}

.card h3 {
  margin: 0 0 8px;
}

.tag {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #38bdf8;
}

.section-title {
  margin: 30px 0 15px;
  font-size: 20px;
  border-left: 4px solid #38bdf8;
  padding-left: 10px;
}

footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px;
  border-top: 1px solid #1e293b;
  margin-top: 30px;
  font-size: 14px;
  opacity: 0.6;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Noticias Nueva Asunción</h1>
  <p>Presidente Hayes · Paraguay</p>
</header>

<nav>
  <a href="#noticias">Noticias</a>
  <a href="#internacional">Internacional</a>
  <a href="#contacto">Contacto</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

  <div class="hero">
    <h2>🌍 Conflicto global en foco</h2>
    <p>Escalada entre EE.UU, Israel e Irán. Petróleo supera USD 100. Tensión en máximos.</p>
  </div>

